# Minimize the Docker build context.
# Only the shared entrypoint is required by every image build; everything
# else is repo metadata (docs, CI, fixtures, schemas) that would needlessly
# inflate the build context and slow down rebuilds.
*

# Allow only what the Dockerfiles actually COPY into images.
!entrypoint/
!entrypoint/**

# Explicitly exclude common heavy paths even if a future rule re-includes them.
.git
.github
.gitignore
docs
tests
scripts
schemas
node
bun
hugo
zola
manifest.json
schemas
security-exceptions.json
analysis_report.md
README.md
SECURITY.md
LICENSE
AGENTS.md
*.md
